data.description: Discover spacious living in this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, complete with a BONUS ROOM, FORMAL LIVING area AND large 3-car garage. Nestled within the highly sought-after community of The Meadows in East Navarre.This meticulously designed home boasts a generous family area with soaring 10' ceilings, a smartly configured split floor plan, and a host of exceptional features.Step outside through triple doors from the family room to a sprawling covered outdoor patio, perfect for year-round living, all within a fully fenced backyard for privacy and security.This residence comes loaded with premium upgrades, including stunning LVP & tile flooring, granite countertops, gleaming stainless steel appliances, and exquisite crown molding throughout.It is a MUST SEE! Don't miss the chance to make it yours today!!
